title: Taliyah's wall is unbearably loud on Definitely not Dominion
body: Title. It's at least twice as loud as it usually is, and other people in the lobby I was in also said that it was really loud. I'm 99% sure that this is a bug.

replies.body: Hi Skyblade79! I'll look into this and see if anything's going on here. Thanks for the report -- having working eardrums is important. :D
